## Stakeholder Communication Workflow

- [ ] 1. Identify all stakeholders and categorize by influence and interest level
- [ ] 2. Determine what each stakeholder needs to know vs. what they want to hear
- [ ] 3. Choose the right communication channel and frequency for each
- [ ] 4. Draft messages that are clear, concise, and action-oriented
- [ ] 5. Align messaging with client objectives and project milestones
- [ ] 6. Build a communication calendar and RACI for the project
- [ ] 7. Review all communications for tone, accuracy, and strategic intent

## Key Inputs
- Project or initiative: {{project}}
- Stakeholder list: {{stakeholders}}
- Key message or update: {{message}}
- Communication goal: {{goal}}
- Client relationship context: {{relationship}}
